{"word":"βοτόν","slug":"βοτόν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βοτόν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βόσκω'><el>βόσκω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a beast</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>: mostly in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>grazing beasts</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; but of birds, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}